    "Details": "A common field refit choice for ER PPC–mounting 'Mechs as much as a way to overcome matériel shortages during the Jihad, the 3T swaps two Magna Hellstar standard PPCs for the advanced models. While reducing range, it also reduces the heat load on the 'Mech's overstressed coolant systems, leading to it being offered as a factory configuration.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Hyper-Extending Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.11</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
